node.text:
🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 | Jack Grealish future update

@jackgrealish future will be decided in the next days as Manchester City are trying to sign him 🔵

- Manchester City are now in direct contact with Aston Villa for Jack Grealish. Talks now ongoing to reach an agreement, still not done/completed. 🌟

- This deal is not gonna take too long as the final decision will be made in the next days between the two clubs. Work in progress. ⏳

- Aston Villa are NOT giving up on Jack and have already offered Grealish a new contract in case he’ll stay at the club. There’s still hope. 🔴

What’s the best decision for Grealish now? 👀👇🏻

#grealish #jackgrealish #mcfc #city #manchester #astonvilla #avfc #england #herewego 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

node.text:
🔴 | OFFICIAL: Varane > Man Utd!

HERE WE GO OFFICIALLY CONFIRMED 🤝🔴

Official statement from #MUFC 🌟📑👇🏻
“Agreement in principle between Manchester United and Real Madrid for Raphaël Varane, confirmed”.

“Manchester United is delighted to announce the club has reached agreement for Raphaël Varane, subject to a medical and to player terms being finalised”. Contract until 2025 + option. ⏳

Medicals expected in the next days, Varane will be in Manchester this week and then he has to follow quarantine rules. Official statement soon. 🇬🇧

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

node.text:
🔵 | Koundé contract and swap deal

EXCLUSIVE: Jules Koundé agreed personal terms with Chelsea until June 2026 and it could be a swap deal with Sevilla! 🇫🇷

- Kurt Zouma has been discussed in the last few hours as part of the deal. He could join Sevilla in the Koundé deal, negotiations ongoing. 🌟

- Contract until June 2026 agreed as Koundé is open to join Chelsea as he wants Champions League football for the next season. 🤝

- Talks ongoing between the two clubs to find an agreement for Jules Koundé to #CFC. 🇬🇧

#chelsea #cfc #kounde #sevilla #juleskounde #transfers #premier #epl #herewego 🌟

node.text:
🔵 | Chelsea open talks for Koundé!

EXCLUSIVE: Chelsea have opened talks with Sevilla for French centre back Jules Koundé 🇫🇷

- Negotiations ongoing between the two clubs to reach an agreement, still not done or agreed. 🔵

- Koundé has a release clause for €80m but Chelsea and Sevilla are discussing to find a solution for a different price. 🗣

- Koundé would be open to accept Chelsea as next club as he wants to play Champions League football, that’s why he was waiting when he received a proposal from Tottenham. 🇪🇺

- Negotiations ongoing for Jules Koundé to Chelsea as next signing after Bettinelli set to join as new goalkeeper from Fulham. 👀

#chelsea #cfc #kounde #sevilla #juleskounde #transfers #premier #epl #herewego 🌟

node.text:
🔴🌟 | Varane details > here we go!

Manchester United are preparing paperworks for Raphaël Varane. DONE deal as reported today and HERE WE GO confirmed. 🔴🤝

- Official announcement after details will be sorted with Real Madrid in the next days. ⏳

- Fee around €50m including add ons as part of the negotiation. Here-we-go. 🚨

- Varane camp still waiting for quarantine rules to decide about medicals, but he’s expected to fly to England this week. ✈️

Matter of days and... Varane will wear this kit! 👕🔴

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

🔴 | Varane > Man Utd HERE WE GO!

Raphaël Varane from Real Madrid to Manchester United, here we go! 🌟🔴 #MUFC #Varane

- Deal almost done and agreement at final stages between Man Utd and Real Madrid, just final details to be completed and then paperworks time. It’s a “matter of hours or days”. 🇫🇷

- Varane has a total agreement with Manchester United on personal terms too, he’s ready. 🤝

- It will take some days for official announcement but Varane is now set to join Manchester United on a permanent deal. ⏳

@raphaelvarane > @manchesterunited...
HERE WE GO! 🔴🤝

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

node.text:
🔴 | Varane and Man Utd updates

Raphaël Varane is getting closer to Manchester United move from Real Madrid! 🇫🇷🌟

- Official bid from Manchester United to Real Madrid for Varane is set to be submitted in the next few days in order to complete the agreement. 🤝

- Manchester United board is now ‘confident’, deal getting closer after direct contacts with Real Madrid but NOT done yet. ⏳

- Varane has an almost ready agreement with Man United on personal terms, just final details to be completed soon. 📑

- Varane is NOT extending his contract [now expiring in June 2022] with Real Madrid because he wants a new challenge, new experience in the Premier League. No other clubs involved as of today, only Manchester United. 🇬🇧

- You will NOT see Varane creating problems to Real Madrid or breaking his relationship with the club. He’s respecting Florentino, the board, Ancelotti and his team-mates. He’ll do his best and train with the team until the two clubs will find an agreement, if the deal will be completed. ⛔️

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego

🇵🇹 | Cristiano future announced!

Juventus vice president Pavel Nedved has just confirmed to @skysport what’s gonna happen for @cristiano this summer 👇🏻⚪️⚫️

“Cristiano Ronaldo will come back on Monday and will STAY with us here at Juventus”. 🔴

How do you rate this decision for Ronaldo? 👇🏻🇵🇹

🔴 | Jadon Sancho... HERE WE GO!

After 16 months negotiations, @sanchooo10 joins @manchesterunited on a permanent deal from Borussia Dortmund. 🤝

- “The chance to join Manchester United is a dream come true and I just cannot wait to perform in the Premier League. This is an exciting squad”. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

- Final fee €85m plus agents fee. Contract until June 2026 signed in the last days with option to extend the deal until June 2027. 🚨

How do you rate this deal? HERE WE GO 👇🏻🔴

node.text:
⚪️ | Harry Kane’s future situation

There’s still no agreement reached now between Manchester City and Tottenham for Harry Kane 🚨

- Tottenham are denying rumours about Harry Kane set to join Manchester City, same from City side. ⚠️

- Daniel Levy wants to keep Kane at the club and the same from Fabio Paratici, there’s nothing agreed between clubs. 🤝

- Manchester City are interested and they consider Harry Kane their main target together with Jack Grealish but NO fee agreed with Spurs. 🔴

- Last bid from Manchester City was one month ago: £100m and players available, turned down by David Levy few days later. ❌

- Harry Kane will talk with Tottenham board and Nuno to discuss about his future soon. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

#thfc #tottenham #spurs #manchestercity #mcfc #city #kane #harrykane #herewego #transfers

node.text:
⚪️ | Tottenham-Sevilla swap deal!

EXCL. Tottenham and Sevilla are now finalizing a new swap deal... then here we go soon! 🤝

- Erik Lamela to Sevilla, Bryan Gil to Tottenham: the agreement is set to be completed on a permanent deal for both players. 🔃

- Sevilla will also receive €25m from Spurs and there will be add ons included in the negotiation. 🇪🇸

What do you think about this swap deal? 👀👇🏻

#sevilla #tottenham #lamela #bryangil #spurs #transfers #sevillafc #thfc #herewego 🇪🇸🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

node.text:
🔴 | Varane’s position on his future

New updates for @raphaelvarane future with Manchester United pushing to sign him 🇫🇷

- Raphaël Varane and his agents confirmed to Real Madrid his desire to try a new experience in the Premier League. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

- Varane will be respectful waiting for the club agreement between Manchester United and Real Madrid, still not completed - but he wants Man United as next challenge. 🔴

- Varane will be respectful with Real Madrid and will NEVER break with the club also if he’s out of contract in 10 months. He’s gonna wait for the to clubs to complete the deal, once the official bid will be on the table soon. 🤝

- Real Madrid were trying again to change his mind... but together with his representatives, Varane also confirmed to Manchester United that he’d be ‘ready’ to accept their contract bid until June 2026 if the agreement will be completed with Real Madrid. Personal terms have never been a problem. ⏳

#realmadrid #varane #mufc #manchester #epl #manchesterunited #real #transfers #herewego
